authoringEnvironment - package authoringEnvironment
Provides the necessary packages (and therefore classes) to create the entire authoring environment.
authoringEnvironment.authoringToolbar - package authoringEnvironment.authoringToolbar
Provides the necessary classes, concrete and abstract, to build the toolbar in the authoring environment.
authoringEnvironment.itemWindow - package authoringEnvironment.itemWindow
Provides the necessary classes, concrete and abstract, to build the item window in the authoring environment - the item window allows users to select which sprites (player, enemey, background, etc) will be included in the game.
authoringEnvironment.mainWindow - package authoringEnvironment.mainWindow
Provides the necessary classes to create the main authoring window, where the user can drag and drop sprites.
authoringEnvironment.settingsWindow - package authoringEnvironment.settingsWindow
Provides the necessary classes to build the settings window - the settings window is where the user can change the properities of the sprite that was most recently clicked on.
AuthoringMenubarCreator - Class in authoringEnvironment.authoringToolbar
This is the creator for the menubar, which allows the user to select new files, add a level, save, or return to the start screen
